&lt;li&gt;Must be a self starter and multi-tasker, while remaining responsible and detail-oriented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
